free-005055880.html">移动设备</a>。对于外行来说，游戏会要求您选择一个具有独特初始武器和技能的角色。你的武器会自动开火。在跑步期间，您唯一拥有的代理是您的移动以及升级时选择升级或新武器或额外津贴。</p><p>跑步持续长达 30 分钟——如果您知道如何在死亡中幸存，则可以持续更长时间。这使得<em>Vampire Survivors</em>成为一款非常适合在上下班途中玩的游戏（或者在任何其他时间，如果我们说实话）。 </p><div id="bc52511bef1d4720971abaa976b4c2d7"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZZZArNBLrsA?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div><p></p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/vampire-survivors-is-getting-four-player-couch-co-op-150809332.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/vampire-survivors-is-getting-four-player-couch-co-op-150809332.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f8856bfd-b824-49d3-8308-fa5950c2e2c4</guid><dc:creator>克里斯霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 21 Jun 2023 15:08:09 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687360187</ingested><modified> 2023-06-21T15:09:50+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="922" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/5aa9ba30-1043-11ee-bfef-8c2b2796a5f6" width="1706"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="922" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/5aa9ba30-1043-11ee-bfef-8c2b2796a5f6" width="1706"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><d