和审讯工人。去年， <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/second-apple-store-to-unionize-oklahoma-city-070056192.html">马里兰州一家苹果商店和俄克拉荷马州另一家苹果商店的员工投票决定成立工会</a>。然而，圣路易斯分公司等其他地点放弃了成立工会的计划，并将其归咎于 Apple 的类似策略。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/apples-union-busting-practices-violated-employee-rights-at-nyc-store-judge-rules-115036323.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apples-union-busting-practices-violated-employee-rights-at-nyc-store-judge-rules-115036323.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> e6a23767-3dd8-4116-a0c5-bef0f8fda10e</guid><dc:creator>莎拉菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 21 Jun 2023 11:50:36 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687347104</ingested><modified> 2023-06-21T11:31:48+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[Unions]]></category><category><![CDATA[Labor Issues]]></category><category><![CDATA[Society & Culture]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="2139" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-01/14faaae0-a7d8-11ed-9fce-ee56dcd49b2b" width="3200"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2139" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-01/14faaae0-a7d8-11ed-9fce-ee56dcd49b2b" width="3200">